steps.html_instructions: Head east on E Myrtle St toward S 5th St

S 5th St turns slightly left and becomes I-55BUS S/S 6th St
Continue to follow I-55BUS S
Take the exit onto I-72 W toward Jacksonville

Keep right at the fork to stay on I-72 W, follow signs for Hannibal
Entering Missouri

Merge onto I-29 N/US-71 N via the ramp to Council Blufffs
Continue to follow I-29 N
Entering Iowa

Merge onto US-77 N/Homestead Expy via the ramp to I-80
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-80 W and merge onto I-80 W

Keep right at the fork to stay on I-80 W
Passing through Wyoming
Entering Utah

Keep right at the fork to stay on I-80 W, follow signs for Reno/S.L. International Airport
Passing through Nevada
